description: Firefighters have put out a brush fire along northbound I-280 in San Francisco, near the Monterey Boulevard onramp.
maintext: Firefighters have put out a brush fire along northbound I-280 in San Francisco, near the Monterey Boulevard onramp.The fire was dangerously close to several homes and vehicles.Firefighters controlled the fire at 11:30 a.m.
title: Brush fire put out along I-280 in San Francisco
